             was indicted for <rs id="t18010701-46-off255" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010701-46-off255" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010701-46-off255" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010701-46-cd256" type="crimeDate">24th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010701-46-off255 t18010701-46-cd256"></join>, four fowls, value 8s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010701-46-victim444" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Amor
                  <interp inst="t18010701-46-victim444" type="surname" value="Amor"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010701-46-victim444" type="given" value="William"></interp>
