                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010701-46-defend442 t18010701-46-punish258"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Lawrence.</p>
